### Flask Schematics Swagger

[![PR](https://github.com/trK54Ylmz/flask-schematics-swagger/actions/workflows/pr.yaml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/trK54Ylmz/flask-schematics-swagger/actions/workflows/pr.yaml)
